<title type="html"><![CDATA[6/ 24 (Thu.) the importance of the ocean/ table topic session(host:Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=509&amp;p=531#p531"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">Place: Zoom Meeting<br />Agenda:<br />07:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />07:05-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />07:40-8:00 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation<br /><br />Let's join the Zoom meeting this Thursday at 07:00 pm<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... 09#success<br /><br />會議 ID:929 8726 6213<br />密碼:112233<br /></span><br /><br />Session I: the importance of the ocean<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.theoceanpreneur.com/impact/ocean-education/seven-reasons-ocean-important/">https://www.theoceanpreneur.com/impact/ ... important/</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://traveltriangle.com/blog/beach-or-mountains/">https://traveltriangle.com/blog/beach-or-mountains/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Why is it so important we need to protect the ocean?<br />2.What do you think Taiwan is doing protecting the ocean? What can we do as individuals?<br />3.Are you a beach person, or mountain person or city person?<br />4.Share a special experience with beach, mountain or city?<br /><br />Second session is ‘Table topic’.<br />First, the host will start by asking one question and point at someone to answer it. After answering it, the person can ask another question, and he has the right to point at someone else to answer his question. It’s like a relay race. So please, each participant prepares some questions in his mind. Speaking time will be strictly controlled. Each answer is for 2 minutes<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因疫情關係，聚會方式改為線上遠距。<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89">AndrewWang</a> — Wed Jun 16, 2021 3:47 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
